These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, romance, disaster, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, punk, ambient, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, british, chinese, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, bike, subway
1. the british is the fan of classical##1
2. the chinese is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching family movies##2
3. the british is the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the fan of folk is on the left of the malaysian##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
8. the malaysian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | family   | satire  | disaster  |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | classical    | folk      | ambient    |
| Nationality   | turkish | british | chinese | malaysian |
| Transport     | subway  | motorbike       | quad-bike    | bike     |

