.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, magic-tricks, sudoku, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, superhero, family, documentary
4 different pets are kept: horse, hamster, goat, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, baseball, cricket, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is between the owner of the goat and the person who's sport is surfing##2
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person watching documentary movies and the owner of the pony##2
7. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
8. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping | magic-tricks    | sudoku  | filmmaking    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie      | superhero  | documentary  | family |
| Pet           | pony      | goat       | hamster      | horse       |
| Sport         | baseball    | snowboarding | cricket | surfing |

