.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, pomegranate, pear, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, chess, dancing, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse, engineer, software-developer
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, boat, scooter
1. the engineer is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the nurse is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person eating garlic is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person eating pear and the nurse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | pomegranate | pear     | garlic   | radish     |
| Hobby       | chess   | reading   | dancing | hiking |
| Job         | entrepreneur   | engineer | software-developer       | nurse    |
| Transport   | boat    | quad-bike | bus  | scooter    |

