.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, security-guard, dressmaker, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, epic, adventure, sports
4 different pets are kept: rat, cat, guinea-pig, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, golf, rowing, weightlifting
 1. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching sports movies is the coach##1
 3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the cat##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is the dressmaker##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the coach is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
10. the security-guard is between the owner of the rat and the musician##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | coach  | musician | security-guard     | dressmaker |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | mystery  | adventure | epic       |
| Pet           | cat       | goldfish    | guinea-pig      | rat           |
| Sport         | surfing | golf   | weightlifting   | rowing         |

