.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, lime, plum, pumpkin
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, journalist, firefighter, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, musical, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, volleyball, cricket, skiing
 1. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 3. the firefighter is the person eating lime##1
 4. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 6. the person eating plum is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the manager is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the journalist is the person watching musical movies##1
 9. the person eating plum is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person watching comedy movies##2
10. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | lime         | plum         | pineapple     | pumpkin      |
| Job           | firefighter | manager | musician    | journalist     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | time-travel       | western    | musical       |
| Sport         | rowing     | cricket       | skiing | volleyball |

