.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, manager, entrepreneur, electrician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, blues, r&b, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, thai, mexican, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, swimming, water-polo
1. the fan of ambient is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the fan of r&b##2
2. the manager is between the fan of ambient and the argentine##2
3. the mexican is between the person who's sport is surfing and the thai##2
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the thai##1
5. the mexican is the mexican##1
6. the thai is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the thai is on the left of the fisherman##1
8. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
9. the fan of blues is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | manager | fisherman  | electrician |
| Music-Genre   | blues      | dubstep       | ambient     | r&b      |
| Nationality   | argentine   | thai      | mexican   | japanese   |
| Sport         | swimming   | water-polo    | baseball | surfing   |

