 5. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 6. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the mexican is the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
10. the japanese is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
