4. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the airplane and the person watching horror movies##2
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
