The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, analyst, mechanic, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, punk, jazz, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, climbing, badminton, weightlifting
 1. the person eating avocado is the mechanic##1
 2. the person eating blueberry is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 3. the mechanic is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 5. the fan of techno is the person eating nectarine##1
 6. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
 9. the journalist is between the security-guard and the person who's sport is soccer##2
10. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
