There 4 different types of food: tomato, peach, lettuce, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, chess, drawing, cooking
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, ferret, fish
 1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person eating tomato is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the person eating tomato and the person eating lettuce##2
 9. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person eating tomato and the person eating lettuce##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | coffee    | cola    | almond-milk      | 7up |
| Food       | tomato        | pumpkin       | lettuce       | peach     |
| Hobby      | drawing | video-games | cooking | chess        |
| Pet        | frog       | fish     | ferret         | guinea-pig           |

