 3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the rat##2
 6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating corn##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the rat is the person driving the trike##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
